- Section-nav anchor wiring across the consolidated tabs: the nav ids in `KeatingUiSettingsTab`, `SpeechSettingsTab`, `LearningTab`, `ProvidersModelsTab`, and `ModelsProvidersTab` all match `settings-section-{id}` targets.
